    ** [SM-1029|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1029] - Bug in HTTP BC when configuring managed keystore for SSL
    ** [SM-1043|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1043] - Poller sends invalid MessageExchange when file has been deleted
    ** [SM-1050|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1050] - Memory Leak in http consumer processor when using SSL


* *Improvement*
    ** [SM-965|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-965] - Allow use of -Dhost, -Dport, -Dusername and -Dpassword on jbi:projectDeploy
    ** [SM-986|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-986] - The maven jbi plugin should not fail it the SU jbi descriptor generation fails but only displays a warning
    ** [SM-1049|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1049] - Raise the number of http requests that can be send concurrently by servicemix-http


* *New Feature*
    ** [SM-958|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-958] - Allow the connections element of the JBI.xml for a Service Assembly to be provided
    ** [SM-1045|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1045] - Servicemix tooling changes to generate JBISharedLibraryDescriptor


* *Task*
    ** [SM-1028|https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/SM-1028] - Ease the release process by avoiding manual changes in the source files

